# API Design Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/api-design.md`**

Key rules:
- REST: nouns for resources, HTTP verbs for actions, plural names
- JSON only unless ADR specifies otherwise; ISO 8601 UTC timestamps
- URL path versioning (`/api/v1/`); breaking changes require a new version
- Consistent error envelope: `{ "error": { "code", "message", "details" } }`

